## Step 4: Configure Label Studio Project

1. Open http://localhost:8080 → **Create Project**
2. Project name: `Protein Secondary Structure Detection`
3. Upload images from `dataset/train/images/` and `dataset/val/images/`
4. Go to **Settings → Labeling Interface → Code** and paste:

```xml
<View>
  <Image name="image" value="$image" zoom="true" zoomControl="true"/>
  <RectangleLabels name="label" toName="image">
    <Label value="alpha_helix"
           background="#FF4444"
           selectedColor="#FF0000"/>
    <Label value="beta_sheet"
           background="#FFD700"
           selectedColor="#FFA500"/>
  </RectangleLabels>
</View>
```

