## Step 8: Generate `train.txt` and `val.txt`

```bash
find $(pwd)/dataset/train/images -name "*.png" | sort > dataset/train.txt
find $(pwd)/dataset/val/images   -name "*.png" | sort > dataset/val.txt

echo "train.txt lines: $(wc -l < dataset/train.txt)"
echo "val.txt lines:   $(wc -l < dataset/val.txt)"
```

